LayoutNode.Content: I ordered this online in walmart website. The plastic wrench tool was cheaper than a $1product. Before I tried to remove a pin in the watch it broke. The back opener had screws keptmoving even after tightening to max. The other type of opener that's supposed to slide into thetiny gap is super thick like a butter knife. The thinnest portion of that tool also wouldnt slide intothat area to pop up the cover. (See 2nd pic)The screwdriver type of tool has a short range thatcannot fit into the diagonal slots of men's watch backside. Topping all these your hands smellof a cheap plastic-rubber combo after trying all these useless tools. First time seeing a pkg withso many defective pieces. See more

LayoutNode.Content: For the price, this package can't be beat. Speaking of beating, don't be rough on the items, it'sdefinitely not built for tough like other lifetime tools. But remember, this was made to fixwatches, not steel construction projects. Besides, you want to be gentle with your watchesanyways to avoid scratches and other possible damage. This value package saved me at least1/2 of what they wanted to charge me at the mall to do that same work. Not only that, I used iton a second watch I also have. Nice to know I have the tools for future occasions when a watchneeds battery replacement. Not only for my watches but for family or friends. This is for suremoney, time and gas saver. Worth the space in my tool box. See more
